Happiest when wearing @monocalle.in 

But more than happy,i am always prouder whenever i am wearing my talented @nimisha_diwakar because to have a vision and also the courage to start your own clothing brand in such a YOUNG AGE is soo remarkable man. Everyone knows about the hardworking, workaholic lady you are but what i love the most is that your clothing reflects the 'angelic' Nimisha's heart and love towards her work. Its beautiful and inspiring. I hope our deals become reality and i am sure you will flourish beyond limits. Also you are not only Nish's angel but an angel in all our life's. Thank you for helping out as always. 💙😘
